Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 5.8 26/62] drm/amdgpu/display: fix ref count leak when pm_runtime_get_sync fails
Date:   Fri, 21 Aug 2020 12:13:47 -0400
Message-Id: <20200821161423.347071-26-sashal@kernel.org>
